Package: com.3dshitwizardfr.vp9tube
Name: VP9Tube
Version: 0.1.0
Architecture: iphoneos-arm64
Description: Bundled VP9 software decoder for YouTube on iOS. Restores 2K/4K VP9 playback on YouTube v20.47.3+ where the built-in decoder was removed.
Maintainer: 3DShitWizardfr
Author: 3DShitWizardfr
Section: Tweaks
Depends: mobilesubstrate (>= 0.9.5000), firmware (>= 14.0)
